data.description: One-story Buffington home with stately stone and brick exterior. Open floorplan with high ceilings and tile and hardwoods in the main areas and master. Wonderful, private outdoor living area with hot tub that overlooks greenspace. Open kitchen with cherry wood cabinetry with center island, white marbled granite counters, built-in stainless appliances. Master suite with upgraded tile shower with bench, walk-in closet, double vanity. Popular Sabine plan. Highpointe is a gated community with world-class amenities and natural gas.
